and somewhere between 9 and 16 points.

NORTH has 13 points. If SOUTH had actually OPENED 1\S, NORTH would insist on game. But SOUTH didn't 
Open, she just Overcalled. So NORTH must be more cautious. He jumps to 3\S and SOUTH shows her 
minimum type hand by passing.}

