With 14 points of his own, NORTH knows his side needs to be in a game somewhere. He passes this information 
to SOUTH with a cue-bid of 2\S.

SOUTH gets the message and starts the hunt for a trump fit by bidding 3\H. That 
makes it easy for NORTH - he bids 4\H.}

