[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/overcalls"]
[Student "S"]
{There is only one reason that WEST should not overcall with 1\S. He is too strong. 
The maximum strength of an overcall is 16 points. Above that you should double.

So WEST doubles, and after EAST bids 2\C, WEST bids 2\S. This shows an overcall 
type hand, but with 17 or more points.

EAST has fine trump support and 8 points so she bids a confident 4\S.}

